# Proposal

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?

Pressure Tracker

## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

It will be an app/program that gathers data from a watch on a person.  With this, it is able to alert the person if their blood pressure is too low/high, can track heart rhythms for certain medical issues.

## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

As noted, the program will track certain heart beats and blood pressure for medical issues such as fainting and seizures from those who suffer from neurological health issues or those from blood pressure.
For this audience, it has been found that with some seizures, the heart can be tracked to slow substantially or possibly stop.  The study I will be referencing will be from those who suffer from
focal epilepsy, where it was found that the monitoring of heart rhythms occured prior to a seizure.  This program will be linked to a smart watch, similar to a fit bit, that tracks heart rhythms. I will set a certain minimum
and maximum number of beats per minute into the code.  When it reaches a certain low/high, it will print out a message to be displayed on the user's phone, alerting them.

